                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The mamlambo has a creature @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed} or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained}, or there is a @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dying]{Dying}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized}, or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} creature within the mamlambo's reach;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mamlambo deals [[/r 2d8+11 #piercing]]{2d8+11 piercing damage} to the creature (<span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Face Eater DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Fortitude</span> save).</p>\n<p>On a failure, the creature also takes an additional [[/r 2d6 #persistent bleed]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Bleed Damage}, or [[/r 4d6 #persistent bleed]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Bleed Damage} on a critical failure.</p>"
